com.karusmc.xmc.core

Class CommandMapProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.karusmc.xmc.core.CommandMapProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.command.CommandMap

    public class CommandMapProxy
extends Object
implements org.bukkit.command.CommandMap
    Acts as a proxy for the Spigot Server instance's internal CommandMap implementation. This class does not modify the internal CommandMap implementation directly to prevent compatability issues with other plug-ins. Allows other classes to listen for command registration updates through implementing the CommandMapObserver interface. Note that classes can only listen to updates done through the CommandMapProxy instance and will not be notified if the command is registered directly through the underlying CommandMap implementation.
    Author:
    PanteLegacy @ karusmc.com
    See Also:
